Pulawy Signs Deal to Purchase Azoty-Adipol From Polish Treasury

-- B y   M a c i e j   M a r t e w i c z
-- 
2011-09-30T08:29:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/pulawy-signs-deal-to-purchase-azoty-adipol-from-polish-treasury.html
Zaklady Azotowe Pulawy SA (ZAP) , a Polish
state-controlled fertilizer maker, signed a preliminary deal to
buy rival Azoty-Adipol SA from the country’s government. Pulawy
didn’t comment on the price in the transaction.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maciej Martewicz at 
 mmartewicz@bloomberg.net  